  "title": "ServiceNow Operations Support (End user / Up to $2700)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a Singaporean to join our client’s team through ES Recruitment as a Systems Administrator (<strong>ServiceNow - End User - Service Request Admin</strong>). This is a 1-year contract position.<br /></p><p>Work Location: <strong>Outram</strong></p><p>Salary range: <strong>$2300 - $2700</strong></p><p><strong>Up to 1 month performance bonus</strong><br /></p><ul><li><p>Responsible for supporting operational systems satisfying contractual Service Level Agreement</p></li><li><p>Perform and manage routine preventive maintenance and operational activities</p></li><li><p>Provide project documentation and reports</p></li><li><p>Monitor and alert base on monitoring tools provided</p></li><li><p>Diagnose and rectify technical issue</p></li></ul><p>Requirement:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Locals (Must cleared both project clearance and pre-employment check)</strong></p></li><li><p>Skills: <strong>Service request admin & End user support</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Experience in End User Environment 1 Year</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Good knowledge and hands-on experience with ServiceNow (hands-on experience with ServiceNow is a strongly preferred)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Excellent written and verbal communication to convey technical ideas to both technical and non-technical audiences and contribute within a team environment</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Pro-active, dynamic and with good analytical/conceptual thinking</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Need to serve 2 months notice if hired for this role</strong><br /></p></li></ul><p>ES Recruitment Pte Ltd (09C4235)</p><p>Hong Chiew Guat (R1219860)</p>",
